---
import { REPO } from '../consts';
---
<section class="block" id="privacy" style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="manifesto reveal">
      <h2>The most private dictation app is the one that <em>can't</em> betray you.</h2>
      <p>Scribe has no backend to breach, no logs to subpoena, and no analytics SDK quietly phoning home. Models run on your hardware; the only network call is the one-time, optional model download. Turn on airplane mode and it still works. That's the proof.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta" style="margin-top:30px">
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href={REPO}>Read the source</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/privacy">Privacy policy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
